chapters.title: Satan turned his wrath on the woman- the Christian Church.
Church and State united in the days of Constantine.
The reformers were persecuted for their faith.
God's church is a spirit filled church that impacts the world.
In an age of irresponsibility God is calling for moral responsibility.
God's church does NOT need the approval of popular religious leaders.
